position":1},"title":"Abu Umamah on Eid: Companions ask Allah to accept good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhammad ibn Ziyad reported: I was with Abu Umamah al-Bahili and others among the Companions of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. When they would return from Eid prayer, they would say to each other, \u201cMay Allah accept good deeds from us and from you.\u201d Imam Ahmad said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25160,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/08\/14\/abu-umamah-on-backbiting\/","url_meta":{"origin":14474,"position":2},"title":"Abu Umamah on Backbiting: Good deeds given to believers backbitten","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 14, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Samarqandi reported: Abu Umamah al-Bahili, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, the servant will be given his record on the Day of Resurrection and he will see good deeds that he had not done. He will say: O Lord, from where does these come? Allah will say: These\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17108,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/09\/three-have-guarantee-from-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14474,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Protection: Three people have a guarantee from Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 9, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThree people have a guarantee from Allah. If he lives he will have provision to suffice him, and if he dies he will enter Paradise: one who enters and greets with peace has a guarantee from\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24930,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/04\/khawarij-violent-worst\/","url_meta":{"origin":14474,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Khawarij: Violent rebels are worst killed under heaven","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 4, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ghalib reported: Abu Umamah, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe khawarij are the worst of those slain under the heavens, and the best of those slain are those who were killed by them. They are the dogs of Hellfire. They were Muslims and then became unbelievers.\u201d I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42180,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/08\/23\/allah-is-one-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14474,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: \u2018Allah is One\u2019 leads to Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGive glad tidings to the people that whoever declares there is no God but Allah, he will have Paradise.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Ku